==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Eating
<hw>Eat"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of
tasking food; the act of consuming or corroding.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Something fit to be eaten; food; <as>as, a peach is
good <ex>eating</ex></as>.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Eating house</b></col>, <cd>a house where cooked
provisions are sold, to be eaten on the premises.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Eau de Cologne</ent>⟦br⟧
